_sText: This is a map that tests the skill using the five-seven, a rarly used gun in the man game, but is much more interesting to use when everyone has one.  Best enjoyed with many people playing, also included in .RAR archive is the same map but renamed gg_desertstorn, this is sp that it can be used with mods such as Gun Game without the problem of there being five-sevens everywhere.  .Nav files are included and it only used standard textures and models.  Have fun!!!
